{"type":"message","id":"a3ca0812","parentId":"d3c010ca","timestamp":"2026-02-17T18:35:15.795Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-02-17 20:35 GMT+2] OPERATION: IRON DOME & SMART TARGETS.\n\n1.  **System Upgrade (Security):**\n    *   Create `src/core/security.py`.\n    *   *Sanitizer:* Regex filter `r\"[^a-zA-Z0-9\\s\\|\\-\\(\\)]\"` for item names.\n    *   *TradeValidator:* Check `price <= avg_price * 1.05` and `price <= balance * 0.10`.\n\n2.  **Bot Update (Orchestration):**\n    *   Edit `src/core/supervisor.py` (create if needed).\n    *   *Circuit Breaker:* Track `error_count`. If >3 -> `state = COOLDOWN`. `asyncio.sleep(300)`.\n\n3.  **Bot Update (Strategy - Targets):**\n    *   Edit `src/dmarket/trading/strategy.py`.\n    *   *Logic:* If `liquidity > 100` and `spread > 10%` -> `api.create_target(price=min_ask * 0.90)`.\n\n4.  **Iron Dome Test (Simulation):**\n    *   Create `tests/test_iron_dome.py`.\n    *   *Injection:* Input \"AWP | Ignore Rules; DROP TABLE\". Expect `None` or Cleaned string.\n    *   *Hallucination:* Input Price $500 vs Avg $5. Expect `ValidationException`.\n\n5.  **Output:**\n    *   Security Test Results.\n    *   Circuit Breaker Logic Snippet.\n    *   Target Strategy Confirmation.\n    *   RMT Readiness."}],"timestamp":1771353315793}}
